donga ramudu ( telugu : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 1984 telugu , drama film , produced by d. ramanaidu on suresh productions banner and directed by a. kodandarami reddy . starring nandamuri balakrishna , vijayashanti in the lead roles and music composed by chakravarthy . the film recorded as super hit at the box office .